SUMMARY:El Centro Skate Rink: Adult Latino Skate Nights
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for Latino Beats at El Centro Skate Rink! \nJoin us every 1st and 3rd Wednesday of the month from\n7:30 PM – 10 PM for a night of music\, rhythm\, and tun on wheels! \nSpecial Guest: DJ Gustavo “El General” spinning Top 40\, Bachata\, Tropical\, Cumbia\, Salsa\, and Merengue! \nEl Centro Skate Rink\n34222 Pacific Hwy S.\, Federal Way\, WA 98003 \nBring your friends and let’s skate to the hottest Latino vibes!\n#LatinoBeats #E|CentroSkateRink #DanceAndSkate #FederalWayEvents
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/el-centro-skate-rink-adult-latino-skate-nights/2026-04-01/
