SUMMARY:Sunset Salsa Wednesdays
DESCRIPTION:The long awaited Waterfront Latin Dance Party with SalsaNow is starting June 5th. Grab your friends and join us every Wednesday this season for an evening of lively music and fun dancing.\nSchedule:\n7 PM FREE Salsa or Bachata Dance Lesson\n8 PM-11 PM DJ\, Music and Dancing\nWhere: Port Covington Marina Pier\, 321 E Cromwell Street\, Baltimore\, MD 21230\n* It is suggested that tennis like shoes (ie Converse\, Toms\, etc.) be worn for best practice.\n* Garage parking is available at 250 Mission Blvd.
