UID:10326601-1775070000-1775084400@golatindance.com
SUMMARY:Salsa Bachata Wednesday - Classes & Social in Houston!
DESCRIPTION:Salsa Wednesday! Join us for Salsa dance lessons in Houston. Everyone welcome. No partner needed. New students 8:30p. Free Social at 9:30p\n\n\nLet’s dance\, practice and have fun! Welcome to our Salsa Night each and every Wednesday in Downtown Houston! Tag your dance partner and be ready to learn some cool and fun social turns and figures in Salsa. \nWe offer 2 levels of dificulty: Intermediates at 7pm. Beginners at 8:30pm. Free social at 9:30pm for all levels! \n🕺 Learn the most sociable dance on earth: Salsa. Each and every Wednesday night! \n🎉 Intermediates: Elevate your Salsa skills with fun combinations. \n💃🏻 Beginners: Learn the foundations of Salsa: steps and fun sociable combos. \n👫 No partner needed! Singles rotate and couples can stay together. All welcome! 18+ \nCOURSE SCHEDULE \n✓ 7:00p. Doors open. Check-in and get a wristband and warm up. \n✓ 7:15-8:30p. Salsa Intermediate: Turns\, combos\, and social figures. Keep improving your leading and following skills with different challenges. Not a class for beginners. Dance experience required. \n✓ 8:30-9:30p Salsa Beginner 1: Learn the basics of Salsa\, basic spot turns\, cross body lead\, leading and following foundations. No Dance experience required. \n✓ 9:30p FREE Salsa Night social dance and party: Everyone is welcome! All levels welcome to the sociall dancing. From the newbie to the pro! Everyone helps each other grow. \n*FAQ: I’m new to dancing\, can I do both beginner and intermdaite class? \nAsnwer: No. You have to go through Beginner 1 material\, Beginner 2 material (Mondays at 8:30pm) and have social dancing experience before you can join Intermediate level. \nHOW TO JOIN / TICKET PRICE \nhttps://bit.ly/salsanightwednesday \n🎟 You can get your tickets online or at the door. \nSALSA INTERMEDIATE \n$20/person per class. \nMember’s Pass Recommended to access this class. \nSALSA BEGINNER 1 \n✓ Salsa Beginner I*: $20/person or $30/couple. \n✓Walk-ins are welcome. \nVENUE LOCATION & PARKING \nHenke & Pillot\, Downtown \n809 Congress St. \nHouston\, TX \n✓ Free street parking around Market Square park. Congress St\, Travis St\, Milan St\, Preston St. \n✓ Cheap garage parking at 805 Franklin St. \n✓ Do not park in commercial and emergency red zones. \n✓ Take your valuables with you or hide them in your trunk out of plain view. \nATTIRE \n✓ Casual / gym / dressy attire welcome. \n✓ If you need dance shoes\, we have discount codes for Fuego Dance Shoes: https://fuegodance.com/discount/GOLD \n✓ Low heels / flats for ladies. \n✓ Leather sole shoes for men. \n✓ Avoid sandals and rubber sole shoes. \n  \nMORE UPCOMING CLASSES & CRASH COURSES \nWe teach Bachata\, Cumbia\, Merengue\, and Kizomba as well. \nLevel 101 aka Beginner 1 is for new students and Level 102 aka Beginner 2 is for returning students. \nLearn more here: https://bit.ly/salsacrashcourse \n  \nMORE UPCOMING PARTIES \nWe also host parties during the weekend so you can dance and practice with all of our students:. \nWeekend classes with parties info: https://bit.ly/weekendparties \n  \nLOVE OUR CLASSES & PARTIES? BECOME A MEMBER! \nLet’s grow our dance community together! \n\nDance as much as you like! We teach 7 days a week in Houston\nWe offer 3 passes: 10 events\, 15 events\, and 20 events.\nPasses do not expire until you redeem all your events.\nThe pass lets you access multiple events: classes\, parties\, and socials at discounted prices.\nGet priority invites to grand openings\, special parties\, and workshops.\nGet the Sunday 1pm Salsa / Bachata Mixer class for free for extra practice and networking / socializing!\nGet extra discounts on Boat parties\, Live band parties\, Private lessons\, and Guest workshops.\nAvoid online tickets fees. You save even more!\n\n  \nCONTACT / FOLLOW US \nChristian Franco\, Dance Instructor \nIG / FB @latindancefactory \nText / WhatsApp: 832-413-2623 for information. \nSe habla Español \nYou can start anytime. There are no contracts or subscriptions. We bring people together to experience the beauty of Latin dancing all over Houston. In no time you will be dancing\, having a blast\, and making new friends. See you on the dance floor. \n  \nLINKS \nCalendar of Events: https://linktr.ee/latindancefactory \nInstagram: https://instagram.com/latindancefactory \nNeed One on One Private Dance Lessons? Book: http://bit.ly/privatedancelessons \nCan’t come to class? Why not learn virtually? https://bit.ly/SalsaAcademyVideos \n  \n#partieseveryday #latindancefactory #salsa #bachata #merengue #cumbia #kizomba #houstontx #livemusic #datenight #nightout #couplelessons #howtodance #newstudents #dancelessons #danceparty #social #salsainhouston #nightlife \n 
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-lessons-for-beginners-wednesday-at-830p-in-houston-01-22/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:Henke & Pillot\, 809 Congress Street\, Houston\, TX 77002\, Houston\, TX\, 77002\, US
CATEGORIES:Houston
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/255619_image.png
END:VEVENT
