DESCRIPTION:🥳METROLATINA Wednesdays🥳\nThe UK’s Longest Running Latin Clubnight\nwith The Latin Collective\nWeekly Wednesdays (running since Mar’ 2001)\n7PM-2AM \n@ BeAtOne GREEK ST\, 17 Greek St\, London W1D 4DR\nClosest tube stations Tottenham Court Rd & #Leicester #Sq 3 minutes walk #Covent #Garden 5 minutes walk \n💃 FREE INTRO SALSA CLASS 7pm\n(to book your place visit https://latincollectiveuk.com/free) \n🍹 Happy hour discounts from 4-8pm\n🍸 2-for-1 on on a range of drinks \n……………………………………………..\n⭐7-7:30PM FREE SALSA INTRO CLASS\n⭐7:30-9:30PM – 2hrs of classes in Xbody Salsa (5 levels) & Bachata (3 levels) \n⭐CLASS PRICES £10 for 1hr (£8 NUS) / £15 for 2hrs (£10 NUS)\nLATIN COLL MEMBERS PAY £13 FOR 2HRS\nor buy our 10 class CLASS PASS (any 10 classes/5 nights in a 2month period at ANY LEVEL) for just £50\nNewBie Passes ((any 10 classes/5 nights in a 2month period AT ABS BEG level) for just £37.50\njoin our membership for FREE via www.latincollectiveuk.com \n⭐CLUBNIGHT DJ till 12AM playing Salsa\, Bachata\, Merengue and more with DJD & guests \nDoor Charge – #Entry is FREE ALL NIGHT\n(bring valid I.D. essential) \n…………………………………………………..\n#DANCE CLASSES\n#FREE intro dance #class 7pm\n…………………………………………………..\n#HAPPY #HOUR – on #cocktails at beers \, spirits + mixer 4-8pm\nUp to 50% #discounts on drinks (except for wine\, fizz\, and bottles of spirits) \n241 on our signature #cocktails ALL #NIGHT\nAll night\n£5 margaritas\n£3 tequila shots\n£15 bottles of wine\n£20 bottle of prosecco \nMore info on www.latincollectiveuk.com.
